
Ranger Help for: enemy dragon
=============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing dragon means your Ranger has sworn against dragons and dragonkin:
scaled monsters, wyrms, drakes, and other ancient reptilian terrors.

This is a dramatic, high-risk identity choice. Dragons are not everywhere,
but when they appear they are often dangerous and memorable.

COMMAND:
  setenemy dragon

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
